'''《彩虹小馬：友情就是魔法》'''（{{lang-en|My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic}}），是[[孩之寶|孩之寶]]同名動畫《[[彩虹小馬：友情就是魔法|彩虹小馬：友情就是魔法]]》的周邊[[漫畫|漫畫]]，由[[IDW公司|IDW公司]]出版，第一冊於2012年11月28日發行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicsalliance.com/2012/07/12/idw-announces-my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic-comic-by-kat/ |title=IDW Announces "My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic" Comic By Katie Cook and Andy Price [SDCC] |first=Chris |last=Sims |publisher=[[Comics_Alliance|Comics Alliance]] |date=2012-07-12 |accessdate=2012-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715012605/http://www.comicsalliance.com/2012/07/12/idw-announces-my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic-comic-by-kat/ |archivedate=2012-07-15 }}</ref>。目前每個月定期連載的為主線系列（Main series）和噩夢騎士系列（Nightmare Knights series）。

孩之寶旗下的《彩虹小馬》從80年代開始已經有幾部動畫和電影，以促進和銷售相關玩具，來到現在已經有四代設計.<ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3633908/Pony-tale.html | title = Pony tale | first = Rebecca | last = Tyrrel | date = 2004-12-24 | accessdate = 2011-11-04 | work = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | archive-date = 2022-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220407181100/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3633908/Pony-tale.html }}</ref><ref name="collectorsweekly">{{cite web | url = http://www.collectorsweekly.com/articles/my-little-pony-smackdown-girls-vs-bronies/ | title = My Little Pony Smackdown: Girls vs. Bronies | date = 2012-06-28 | accessdate = 2012-06-28 | work = [[Collectors_Weekly|Collectors Weekly]] | first = Lisa | last = Hix | archive-date = 2012-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120630190625/http://www.collectorsweekly.com/articles/my-little-pony-smackdown-girls-vs-bronies/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

